    "levelAdaptation": "<div><p>After level 5: +D6 damage, +10 Combat Skill, +1 Armor (all Hit Locations except Chest)</p></div><div><p>After level 10: +10 Health, +D8 damage</p></div>",
    "actions": [
      {
        "startDie": 1,
        "endDie": 2,
        "name": "Rusting Slash (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Desiccated Cryptguard swings its corroded sword at a target, aiming to weaken their armor. It makes a melee attack, dealing D6 Slashing damage on a hit. If the attack hits, the target must immediately make an Armor Integrity check, as their armor begins to rust and deteriorate.</p></div>"
      },
      {
        "startDie": 3,
        "endDie": 4,
        "name": "Relentless Assault (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Desiccated Cryptguard moves forward with a determined stride, attempting to overwhelm a target with multiple strikes. It makes two melee attacks against the same target, dealing D4+1 Slashing damage for each hit.</p></div>"
      },
      {
        "startDie": 5,
        "endDie": 6,
        "name": "Tomb Guardian's Wrath (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Desiccated Cryptguard channels its guardian spirit and delivers a powerful strike imbued with unholy energy. It makes a melee attack, dealing D6 Slashing damage. If the attack hits, the target must succeed on a Resolve check or become Frightened (20).</p></div>"
      }
    ],
    "description": "<div><p>Desiccated Cryptguards are skeletal sentinels tasked with guarding the sacred resting place of ancient Vaelorian nobility. Their skeletal forms are draped in tattered remnants of armor, once a symbol of valor and protection, now corroded and withered by the passage of time. When intruders dare to trespass, the Desiccated Cryptguards rise from their slumber and unleash relentless attacks upon those who seek to desecrate the crypt's sanctity.</p></div>",
